node.text:
I’m proud to be a brand ambassador for a Black woman owned tech company @myavanahaircare, a new destination for healthy hair care. MYAVANA makes your hair life easier with their new mobile app. Simply take a photo of your hair and get instantly matched to the products that will give you the best results. Save time, money, and feel confident having the hair that you love. The app also gives you access to: also gives you access to: - Chat with a personal hair consultant
- Video content for healthy hair guidance
- Hair kit for a deeper hair analysis
✨
Follow @myavanahaircare now and click the link in their bio to Download + Subscribe to the new mobile app! ✨
#SupportBlackBusiness
#BuyBlack
#WomenSupportingWomen
#MyavanaHairCare

#Repost @ludacris ・・・
With States Starting to Reopen & Schools Letting Out How Do We ENSURE the Safety of Our Children? By First Reinforcing Hygiene as a PRIORITY! AND This Time In a FUN WAY! Listen To The KIDS SPEAK for Themselves because We NEED THIS NOW MORE THAN EVER! To watch the full Video Click the Link in My bio and follow @kidnation NOW! Help Share This Positive Life Changing Message with everyone you Can 🙏🏾 #stayclean #kidnation
